<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907997>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Map showing the type locality (red pentacle) and the known locality (red circle) of Smithophis linearis sp. nov. in Yingjiang County, Yunnan Province, China and Huton [now Hutung], Bhamo District, Kachin State, Myanmar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907999>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. The type locality habitat of Smithophis linearis sp. nov. in the vicinity of Tongbiguan National Nature Reserve, Nabang Town, Yingjiang County, Yunnan Province, China. A. hilly evergreen forest. B. Stream where the holotype was found. Photographs by Mian Hou (A) and Yin-lei DU (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907999/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3908001>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., paratype ZSIK 4194. Entire specimen in approximately dorsal view (above) and head in dorsal, ventral and right lateral (below, left to right) views. Scale bar = 10 cm. Photographs by V. Deepak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3908001/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3908003>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., paratype BMNH 1925.12.22.41. Entire specimen in dorsal view (above) and head in dorsal, ventral and left lateral (below, left to right) views. Scale bar = 10 cm. Photographs by V. Deepak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3908003/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3908005>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., paratype BMNH 1925.12.22.42. Entire specimen in dorsal view (above) and head in dorsal, ventral and right lateral (below, left to right) views. Scale bar = 10 cm. Photographs by V. Deepak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3908005/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907991>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., holotype (KIZ 059110), TL: 609 mm. A. anals and B. subcaudals on ventral view of tail. Photographs by Mian HOU." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907991/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907993>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., holotype (KIZ 059110), TL: 609 mm. A–B. Lateral, C. front, D. ventral, and E. dorsal view of head. Photographs by Mian HOU." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907995>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Smithophis linearis sp. nov., holotype (KIZ 059110), TL: 609 mm. A. dorsal, B. Lateral and C. ventral view of skull. Photographs by Jing-song SHI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

